snippet: Rafael Nadal defeated Andy Murray, 6-4, 6-1, for his second straight victory at the ATP World Tour Finals in London and a spot in the semifinals.
abstract: Rafael Nadal defeats Andy Murray to advance to semifinals of ATP World Tour Finals tennis tournament.
lead_paragraph: Rafael Nadal defeated Andy Murray, 6-4, 6-1, for his second straight victory at the ATP World Tour Finals in London and a spot in the semifinals.

headline.main: Nadal Advances in London; Ferrer Is Eliminated
